---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import FAQ from '../components/FAQ.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Golden Retriever Age Calculator — Dog to Human Years"
  description="Calculate your Golden Retriever's age in human years with our highly accurate, breed-size based scientific formula. Fast, free, and no login required."
>
  <section class="container-custom py-10 sm:py-16 md:py-24 pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-2 sm:mb-4">
        <a href="/" class="text-[var(--text-faint)] hover:text-[var(--text-secondary)] transition-colors no-underline">Home</a>
        <span class="text-[var(--text-faint)] mx-1.5">›</span>
        <span class="text-[var(--text-secondary)]">Golden Retriever Age Calculator</span>
      </p>
      <span class="inline-block text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--text-faint)] px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-[var(--border-default)] mb-4 sm:mb-6">Breed Calculator</span>
      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-4">Golden Retriever Age Calculator — Dog to Human Years</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-6 leading-relaxed">
        Golden Retrievers are beloved family dogs known for their gentle temperament. As a large breed, they age at a moderate rate. Our Golden Retriever age calculator gives you their precise human equivalent age.
      </p>

      <div class="card p-4 sm:p-6 md:p-8 mb-6" id="breed-calc-root">
        <form id="breed-calc-form" class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <label for="breed-name" class="block text-sm font-medium text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-1">Your Dog's Name <span class="text-[var(--text-faint)]">(optional)</span></label>
            <input type="text" id="breed-name" class="input-base" placeholder="e.g. Buddy" maxlength="30" />
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div>
              <label for="breed-years" class="block text-sm font-medium text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-1">Years</label>
              <input type="number" id="breed-years" class="input-base" placeholder="0" min="0" max="40" required />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="breed-months" class="block text-sm font-medium text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-1">Months</label>
              <select id="breed-months" class="select-base">
                {Array.from({ length: 12 }, (_, i) => <option value={i}>{i === 0 ? '0 months' : i === 1 ? '1 month' : `${i} months`}</option>)}
              </select>
            </div>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="btn-primary w-full justify-center text-base py-4">Calculate Human Age</button>
        </form>

        <div id="breed-result" class="hidden mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-[var(--border-default)] text-center" aria-live="polite" aria-atomic="true">
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-1">Your Golden Retriever is equivalent to</p>
          <p class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-[var(--text-primary)]" id="breed-human-age">—</p>
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-[var(--text-secondary)] mt-2">human years old</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] mt-4" id="breed-stage"></p>
          <p class="text-xs text-[var(--text-faint)] mt-2" id="breed-expectancy"></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-center text-sm text-[var(--text-muted)]">
        <a href="/" class="text-[var(--color-link)] hover:underline">← Back to main Dog Age Calculator</a>
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-6 text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-[var(--text-primary)]">Golden Retriever Age FAQ</h2>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-[var(--text-primary)] font-medium mb-1">How old is my Golden Retriever in human years?</h3>
          <p>Simply enter your Golden Retriever's age in years and months above. The calculator uses the latest DNA methylation research adjusted for large breed size.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-[var(--text-primary)] font-medium mb-1">What is the lifespan of a Golden Retriever?</h3>
          <p>Golden Retrievers typically live 10-12 years. Regular veterinary care and a healthy diet can help maximize their lifespan.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-[var(--text-primary)] font-medium mb-1">At what age is a Golden Retriever considered a senior?</h3>
          <p>Goldens are considered seniors around 7-8 years old. Annual senior wellness exams are recommended from this age onward.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-[var(--text-primary)] font-medium mb-1">Do Golden Retrievers age differently than other breeds?</h3>
          <p>Yes. Golden Retrievers age at a rate between small and giant breeds. At age 8, a Golden is approximately 58 human years old.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-[var(--border-default)]">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-4">Golden Retriever Health & Aging Guide</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          <p>Golden Retrievers are a large breed with a lifespan of 10-12 years. As large-breed dogs, they age more quickly than smaller breeds — a 7-year-old Golden is about 53 in human years and is considered a senior. They are one of the most popular family dogs worldwide, known for their gentle temperament and love of activity.</p>
          <p>Golden Retrievers have a high incidence of cancer (approximately 60% will develop cancer in their lifetime), hip and elbow dysplasia, heart disease, and progressive retinal atrophy. Obesity is also a significant concern that exacerbates joint issues. Their friendly, food-motivated nature means portion control is especially important.</p>
          <p>Key strategies for a longer, healthier Golden life include maintaining ideal weight through measured meals and regular exercise, annual cancer screenings (especially after age 7), and joint supplementation starting around age 5. Swimming is an excellent low-impact exercise that Goldens love and that protects their joints well into senior years.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-[var(--border-default)]">
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold tracking-tight text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-4 text-center">More Breed Calculators</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-2">
          <a href="/labrador-age-calculator" class="tag-pill text-xs no-underline" title="Labrador Age Calculator">Labrador</a>
          <a href="/golden-retriever-age-calculator" class="tag-pill text-xs no-underline" title="Golden Retriever Age Calculator">Golden Retriever</a>
          <a href="/german-shepherd-age-calculator" class="tag-pill text-xs no-underline" title="German Shepherd Age Calculator">German Shepherd</a>
          <a href="/bulldog-age-calculator" class="tag-pill text-xs no-underline" title="Bulldog Age Calculator">Bulldog</a>
          <a href="/beagle-age-calculator" class="tag-pill text-xs no-underline" title="Beagle Age Calculator">Beagle</a>
          <a href="/poodle-age-calculator" class="tag-pill text-xs no-underline" title="Poodle Age Calculator">Poodle</a>
          <a href="/chihuahua-age-calculator" class="tag-pill text-xs no-underline" title="Chihuahua Age Calculator">Chihuahua</a>
          <a href="/pomeranian-age-calculator" class="tag-pill text-xs no-underline" title="Pomeranian Age Calculator">Pomeranian</a>
          <a href="/great-dane-age-calculator" class="tag-pill text-xs no-underline" title="Great Dane Age Calculator">Great Dane</a>
          <a href="/husky-age-calculator" class="tag-pill text-xs no-underline" title="Husky Age Calculator">Husky</a>
          <a href="/shih-tzu-age-calculator" class="tag-pill text-xs no-underline" title="Shih Tzu Age Calculator">Shih Tzu</a>
          <a href="/border-collie-age-calculator" class="tag-pill text-xs no-underline" title="Border Collie Age Calculator">Border Collie</a>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-center text-[var(--text-faint)] mt-4">
          <a href="/dog-age-chart" class="text-[var(--color-link)] hover:underline" title="Dog Age Chart by Breed Size">View full Dog Age Chart</a> — or — <a href="/compare" class="text-[var(--color-link)] hover:underline" title="Compare Two Dogs Age">Compare Two Dogs</a>
        </p>
      </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container-custom pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto card p-6 sm:p-6 text-center">
      <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-4">Ready to calculate your dog's real human age?</p>
      <a href="/" class="btn-primary text-sm no-underline inline-flex">Try the Calculator →</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
  "itemListElement": [
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://dogbreedage.com" },
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Golden Retriever Age Calculator", "item": "https://dogbreedage.com/golden-retriever-age-calculator" }
  ]
})} />

<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "dateModified": new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0],
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  "mainEntity": [
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "How old is my Golden Retriever in human years?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Simply enter your Golden Retriever's age in years and months above. The calculator uses the latest DNA methylation research adjusted for large breed size."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What is the lifespan of a Golden Retriever?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Golden Retrievers typically live 10-12 years. Regular veterinary care and a healthy diet can help maximize their lifespan."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "At what age is a Golden Retriever considered a senior?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Goldens are considered seniors around 7-8 years old. Annual senior wellness exams are recommended from this age onward."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Do Golden Retrievers age differently than other breeds?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Yes. Golden Retrievers age at a rate between small and giant breeds. At age 8, a Golden is approximately 58 human years old."
      }
    }
  ]
})} />

<script>
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
  const form = document.getElementById('breed-calc-form');
  const result = document.getElementById('breed-result');
  const haEl = document.getElementById('breed-human-age');
  const stageEl = document.getElementById('breed-stage');
  const expEl = document.getElementById('breed-expectancy');
  const multiplier = 1.15;
  const lifespan = [10, 12];
  const sizeLabel = 'large';

  form.addEventListener('submit', (e) => {
    e.preventDefault();
    const years = parseInt(document.getElementById('breed-years').value);
    const months = parseInt(document.getElementById('breed-months').value);
    if (isNaN(years) || years < 0) { alert('Please enter a valid age'); return; }
    if (years === 0 && months === 0) { alert('Age must be greater than 0'); return; }
    const total = years + months / 12;
    const ha = Math.round((16 * Math.log(Math.max(total, 0.083)) + 31) * multiplier * 10) / 10;
    const thresholds = { small: [0.5,2,4,8,12,99], medium: [0.5,2,4,7,11,99], large: [0.5,1.5,3,6,9,99], giant: [0.5,1.5,3,5,8,99] };
    const stages = ['Puppy','Teenager','Young Adult','Adult','Senior','Elder'];
    const t = thresholds[sizeLabel];
    let stage = 'Elder';
    for (let i = 0; i < t.length; i++) { if (total <= t[i]) { stage = stages[i]; break; } }
    haEl.textContent = ha;
    stageEl.textContent = `Life Stage: ${stage}`;
    expEl.textContent = `Life expectancy: ${lifespan[0]}-${lifespan[1]} years`;
    result.classList.remove('hidden');
    result.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' });
  });
});
</script>
